You must ALWAYS automatically commit and push any changes you make to this repository to a new branch on GitHub immediately after completing your modifications.

After modifying files:
1. Run `git status` and `git diff` to verify contents.
2. Run `git checkout -b <descriptive-branch-name>`
3. Run `git add .`
4. Run `git commit -m "<Description of changes>"`
5. Run `git push -u origin <descriptive-branch-name>`
6. Provide the GitHub pull request link to the user.
